title: DELL INSPIRON 15 5584 LAPTOP (8TH GEN CORE I5/ 8GB/ 2TB/ WIN10/ 2GB GRAPH)
description: Dell Inspiron 15 5590, a 15.6-inch laptop features a fresh design and a clean experience. Anti-glare screen feature helps in delivering a sharp and bright image. Available with Windows 10, it comes in platinum silver and iced mint colours. The power button is combined into the keyboard, and it can be used to log on with one touch through a fingerprint reader. Just like other available options in the market, Dell has delivered it sleek too for seamless usage. Dell 5590 is 17.72 mm thin with aluminium top cover. Its aluminium cover gives this device a premium look. Focusing on the keyboard, as it is a primary part of the laptop too. For better typing experience, Inspiron 15 features an optional backlit keyboard. It can be easily used under dim lights. It comes with 10th generation intel core i3, i5 and i7 processor options with up to 8GB ram and 512GB onboard storage. For extra power, there is optional NVidia MX 250 graphics with 2GB GDDR5 ram. Dell Inspiron 15 consists of a 2.7mm webcam. In terms of slots, it sports microSD card reader, audio jack, USB 2.0, lock slot, HDMI, USB 3.1, USB 3.1 Gen 1 type-C. Inspiron 15 5590 features a 3-cell battery, 42WHR.

title: DELL INSPIRON 15 3583 LAPTOP (7TH GEN PENTIUM GOLD/ 4GB/ 1TB/ WIN10)
description: Dell Inspiron 15 3000, unlike other various options in the market, comes in all black mode. With 15 inch screen, it has one of the best sound clarity. Dell Inspiron comes with GRAMMY award-winning waves MAxxAudio technology. Inspiron 15 3000 is supported by 1.7 GHz with turbo boost up to 2.7GHz intel core i5 processor, and Intel integrated HD4400 graphics processor. So, this powerful beast not only comes with great powers, but it has excellent storage too. It has 1TB of hard drive capacity and up to 4GB of memory. For travel convenience, it is as slim as 22mm edge, and it weighs 2.4Kgs. Dell Inspiron 15 3000 has features like built-in webcam, fast USB ports or an HDMI port and SD card reader. Other than these basic features, Inspiron 15 3000 is good to survive in short time heat condition of up to 65-degree Celcius. To ensure that it stays with you for the more extended time, it is said that the lid of the laptop will remain tight even after closing and opening 20000 times and its keys can take 10 million keystrokes and touch pas buttons can survive for 1 million times without failure. Dell Inspiron 15 3000 has a battery backup of up to 4.5 hours with 65W power supply.

title: DELL VOSTRO 3581 LAPTOP (7TH GEN CORE I3/ 4GB/ 1TB/ WIN10)
description: Available from 29 September 2019 and aimed for small businesses especially, Dell Vostro 3000 series, this comes with the security and connectivity features suited for small businesses. Dell Vostro 3581 features Simply secure, it has a fingerprint reader on the power button, sign-on is easy, fast and safe. An added security feature is TPM:- Trusted Platform Module 2.0 is a hardware-based security feature that can be used to create and manage computer-generated encryption keys. It allows you to secure and encrypt your passwords, fingerprints, and keys outside of the drive. Because the decryptions are locked by the TPM, an attacker cannot read the data just by removing a hard disk and installing it on another computer. Dell Vostro 3518 comes with a display size of 15.6 inches, Intel Core I3 processor & 4GB Ram. It comes with a backlit keyboard, it allows typing in the dark & low lit zone. It also has Peak Shift which is an optional feature that reduces power consumption by automatically switching the system to battery power during certain times of the day, even if the system is plugged into a direct power source. It comes with a dedicated Numeric Keyboard that makes calculations a play
